B026C040V035	26	40	35	After he brought mee to the North gate, and measured it, according to these measures,
B026C040V036	26	40	36	The chambers thereof, the postes thereof, and the arches thereof, and there were windowes therein round about: the height was fiftie cubits, and the breadth fiue and twentie cubites.
B026C040V037	26	40	37	And the postes thereof were towarde the vtter court, and palme trees were vpon the postes thereof on this side, and on that side, & the going vp to it had eight steps.
