B026C041V010	26	41	10	And betwene the chambers was the widenes of twentie cubites round about the House on euery side.
B026C041V011	26	41	11	And the doores of the chambers were toward the place that remained, one doore toward the North, and another doore toward the South, and the breadth of the place that remained, was fiue cubites round about.
